            <div type="transcript" id="F611A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Her sweet Weight on my<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Heart a Night</l>
                    <l>Had scarcely deigned to lie - </l>
                    <l>When, stirring, for Belief's<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 delight, </l>
                    <l>My Bride had slipped<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 away - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If 'twas a Dream - made<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 solid - just</l>
                    <l>The Heaven to confirm - </l>
                    <l>Or if Myself were dreamed of Her - </l>
                    <l>The power to presume - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>With Him remain - who unto Me - </l>
                    <l>Gave - even as to All -</l>
                    <l>A Fiction superseding Faith - </l>
                    <l>By so much - as 'twas real - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
